FLEX CONTAINER:
flex-direction: row-reverse, column-reverse

FLEX ITEMS:

display: flex

flex: short for flex-grow, flex-shrink and flex-basis

justify-content: center, flex-start, flex-end, space-around, space-between, space-evenly
(NOTE - justify-content aligns on the horizontal axis)

align-items: center, flex-start, flex-end, stretch, baseline
(NOTE - align-items aligns on the vertical axis)

flex-direction: column and row 
(NOTE - When flex direction is changed to column, justify-content becomes vertical axis
and align-items becomes horizontal)

flex-wrap: wrap

flex-direction: column, row

order: default is 0, can be amended to - or + to change order

gap: set at px - places gaps of desired size between flex items

